ating, rather than being suppressed by our UK-hating Establishment. What&#8217;s not to like? Don&#8217;t you know that people like to feel good about themselves, not be lectured constantly about how they have so much to learn from woman and gay hating third world cultures? All cultures are NOT equal. And yes, we are living in a tyranny. We now lock up harmless British people for having ill advised drunken solitary rants and the crime of using BAD words while refusing to investigate violent crimes and funding Muslim organisations that want to obliterate our culture &#8211; see the source of funding for the Woolwich murderers prayer meetings. The only people who ever get deported in Britain are British people to face persecution in the US and EU for acts that are not crimes in the UK. Andew Simeou? Gary MacKinnon? Our Establishment has lost the plot. it&#8217;s insane &#8211; it actually seems to hate all British people and want to stamp them out. What did we do that was so bad? Hence ukip. Take your head out of your behind and go and meet some real people before you embarrass yourself any more.</p>
