        <div id="dsq-comment-body-278011" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-278011" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>It might be your point but it&#8217;s not mine. You are mixing up methods and aims again. Left and right wing extremists wish to impose utopias on us and therefore use an overbearing state. However, Hitler had a very different vision of society to the socialists, as I have outlined.</p>
