        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-278061" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-278061" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>You are confusing economic left and right, with racism.</p>
<p>Left = Big state, National Control, Big Brother, Perfect (state) monopoly, State propaganda replaces education, Unionised power center, committees and corruption. lowest common denominator of standards, targets elimination of risk &#8211; and has failed in every single implementation. Mao, Stalin, Hitler, Brown</p>
<p>Right = Free Markets, freedom of choice, perfect competition, High standards of education, private healthcare, Embrace of Risk, Strong Leadership rather than committee, Adam Smith, Hayak, Thatcher, Churchill.</p>
<p>Racism is caused by a group of people feeling threatened by another group of people on home turf.</p>
<p>The latter has nothing to do with the former two.</p>
</div>
