        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-219101" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-219101" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Matthew &#8211; Get out of London some time. You will find the appetite for the metrpolitan liberal elite is a lot less than it is in Camden and Islington.  Then think where UKIP is going.</p>
</div>
