        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-219381" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-219381" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Adding fuel to the fire, the last time the media had a drawn-out +ve story was under Tony Blair, 1997-2004, only a very small part of which actually worked.  Buildings-wise and House of Lords-wise of course.  And employment rights; wage-wise.  Other small potatoes given what we now face but great even as a relatively young right-leaner in politics.  I don&#8217;t count that big society or I might laugh for a good few hours.</p>
