            <div id="dsq-comment-message-219501" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>The EU may not be as violently oppressive as the EU, but it is certainly a tyranny.<br />
How else can you describe an organisation that has no democratic legitimacy, but felt it had the right to depose two elected Prime Ministers in order to protect itself.<br />
