Listen-up, UKIPers, the Westminster Establishment will pound the alarm of negativity against you; continuously moving from one policy,  to the next.  Some policies,  even have &#8216;seasons&#8217; for how effective they are on brainwashing the public. George Gunn, and Mike Small have a &#8216;related&#8217; articles you should read on Bella-ra-Fella.<br />
Matthew, the writing is on the wall; UKIP are the first of the new far right parties,  that will gain popularity, and pace; the Westminster Establishment cannot hold back the surging tide of electoral resentment. We are witnessing the beginning of a new political era for Britain. Westminster is dead,  long live the people. </p>
