            <div id="dsq-comment-message-219821" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>The media/political class is so ensconced in its PC comfort zone that it&#8217;s become completely blinded by its own contorted rhetoric, and it now genuinely seems to believe that the EDL committed last week&#8217;s murders &#8211; we can&#8217;t actually kick anyone at all from our country because of the Human Rights Act and the ECHR principles it prioritises &#8211; and now the EU&#8217;s going beserk because we dare to offer different benefits to Brits compared to foreigners.</p>
