                <span id="dsq-author-user-219951">Abhay</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-219951" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-219951" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Why is Parris upset with UKIP? What is wrong if UKIP is providing conservatives with an electoral option? His vituperations against UKIP are a whole lot of froth. He should try and do something to improve the Tory culture, if he can and not waste his time.</p>
</div>
        </div>

    <ul class="children">
    <li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="dsq-comment-220701">
