            <cite id="dsq-cite-220701">
                <span id="dsq-author-user-220701">Colonel Mustard</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-220701" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-220701" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>I suspect it has more to do with UKIP&#8217;s policy towards gay marriage rather than anything else.</p>
</div>
        </div>

