            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-220391" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-220391" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Nothing new so far, the right honorable journalist is so enamored with his version of reality which makes him utterly blind to certain on-goings that must be interpreted in a much wider context.</p>
