                <span id="dsq-author-user-220401">maurice12brady</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-220401" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-220401" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>When one considers the amount of crap that could (should!) be written about third-rate journos like you &#8212; remember living on dole-money for your failed stunt &#8212; so put a sock in it Parris &#8212; people in glass houses etc.</p>
</div>
