            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-220471" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-220471" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>A re-reading of Prof. John Carey’s book The Intellectuals and the Masses goes a long way to explaining the why UKIP has so violently exercised the bowels of our political elites.  A very funny and naughty review of the work may be enjoyed thanks to the Grumpy Old Bookman.  link below.</p>
<p><a href="http://grumpyoldbookman.blogspot.co.uk/search?q=carey" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-comment','http://grumpyoldbookman.blogspot.co.uk']);" rel="nofollow">http://grumpyoldbookman.blogspot.co.uk/search?q=carey</a></p>
</div>
