        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-220831" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-220831" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Try reading the article. Read it aloud to yourself whilst tracing a finger under every word, if that helps you.</p>
