                <span id="dsq-author-user-221511">JustAnOtherRandomGit</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-221511" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221511" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>You&#8217;re not complaining about falling standards in grammar and language education, by any chance?  It sounds like you might feel positively at home in UKIP &#8230;</p>
