            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-221861" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221861" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Fascist needs  a &#8216;Duce&#8217; to lead them; someone who is always going on about the military virtues and war.  Nigel Farage just does not fill the bill.  Even William Haigh, of all people, is more eager for military adventures than Nigel.</p>
