        <div id="dsq-comment-body-221301" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221301" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Surely resolutely refusing to believe that the 1950s have gone, never to return, is somewhat fanciful but far from extreme?</p>
