<p>They CLAIM to think this. If they were faced with a choice between living in the UK, in the EU, or in North Korea, I imagine they might see the EU as looking less tyrannical.</p>
<p>What sort of comment do you expect from people constantly trying to sound more extreme than each other?</p>
