        <div id="dsq-comment-header-221571" class="dsq-comment-header">
            <cite id="dsq-cite-221571">
                <span id="dsq-author-user-221571">walterellis</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-221571" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221571" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>That sounds reasonable, JANRG. We are agreed that UKIP voters are a minority and that, within that minority, there is a nasty fringe. Let&#8217;s hope that Cameron can actually get some business done with Merkel. Even the French are getting restive.</p>
<p>Is it really human nature to be rude and abusive behind the cloak of anonymity? If so, that&#8217;s a sad comment on human nature.</p>
</div>
