        <div id="dsq-comment-body-221581" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221581" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Dunno.  I think all of us get misanthropic occasionally, and take opportunities for release when we can.  It probably is better to do this in real life and under our own name.</p>
