            <div id="dsq-comment-message-221711" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Some people favour a political set-up that is imposing extreme hardship on the peoples of Greece, Spain, Portugal  and Ireland.  They call themselves europhiles; apparently they love Europe but not the people who live there.  They think of themselves as moderates; the extremists are those who oppose them.</p>
